list.comment: Made OrderServer abstract and created two new classes that extend from it: OrderServerSimulatedInternal and OrderServerRealExternal OrderServerRealExternal not implemented yet - has empty methods

task.summary: 2020/11/15: Added CommonGUI.java Added Development log.txt to project Changed InterActiveBrokersAPI constructor to private and made a singleton accessor. Made EClientSocket in InterActiveBrokersAPI private Added getPosOrdersObservableList to MainModelThread.PosOrdersManager changed ControllerPositionsWindow.printout() to synchronized Added MikeSimLogger and updated .gitignore Updated javadoc in documentation Before moving CommonGUI from prototype to controllerandview

Added new module CustomFXMLs - this can be used in SceneBuilder. The .jar file which the module produces after choosing "build artifacts" has to be added to the MikeSimNoGradle module for it to work.
Now tracking and managing development at Youtrack: https://mstawowy.myjetbrains.com/youtrack/agiles/120-2/current?issue=MSim-3
Commiting before attempting to refactor according issue MSim-3
Made OrderServer abstract and created two new classes that extend from it: OrderServerSimulatedInternal and OrderServerRealExternal OrderServerRealExternal not implemented yet - has empty methods
Starting work on MSim-14 and MSim-15. Cleaned up MikePosOrders a little bit. Starting to create comments for main classes. Updated gitignore to exclude JavaDoc files from diff view.
